| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6982 — Recovery Inhibition (securotrop)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: a0a70f8e-5411-549f-963a-3a1c7bc0d20c"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
